---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Shipping Information">
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container" style={{ maxWidth: '800px', margin: '0 auto' }}>
      <div class="ui-section-header">
        <div>
          <span class="ui-eyebrow">Logistics</span>
          <h2>Shipping Information</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="prose">
        <h3>UK Delivery</h3>
        <p>All our soaps are hand-cut and packaged in our Edinburgh studio. We aim to dispatch all orders within 1-2 working days.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Standard Delivery (Royal Mail 2nd Class):</strong> £3.95 (2-3 working days)</li>
          <li><strong>Express Delivery (Royal Mail 1st Class):</strong> £4.95 (1-2 working days)</li>
          <li><strong>Free Standard Delivery:</strong> On all UK orders over £30.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>International Delivery</h3>
        <p>Currently, we only ship within the UK. As a small-batch producer, keeping our footprint local allows us to ensure the quality and freshness of our cold-pressed bars.</p>

        <h3>Packaging</h3>
        <p>We believe in radical transparency and sustainability. Your order will arrive in 100% recyclable and compostable packaging. No plastic tape, no bubble wrap, ever.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose { color: var(--clr-text-muted); font-size: var(--text-base); line-height: 1.7; }
  .prose h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--clr-text); margin-top: var(--sp-8); margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); font-weight: 400; }
  .prose p { margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); }
  .prose ul { padding-left: var(--sp-5); margin-bottom: var(--sp-6); }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: var(--sp-2); }
  .prose strong { color: var(--clr-text); font-weight: 600; }
</style>
